results.abstract: Stafford, Thomas P (Maj Gen): Named Air Force deputy chief of staff for research and development (S)
results.snippet: EDWARDS AIR FORCE BASE, Calif., Feb. 25 (AP)--Maj. Gen. Thomas P. Stafford of the Air Force, who spent more than 500 hours in space, has been nominated by President Carter to be deputy chief of staff of the Air Force for research and development.
results.lead_paragraph: EDWARDS AIR FORCE BASE, Calif., Feb. 25 (AP)--Maj. Gen. Thomas P. Stafford of the Air Force, who spent more than 500 hours in space, has been nominated by President Carter to be deputy chief of staff of the Air Force for research and development.
